{
  "stem": "166.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we marched through the bridge there, and I seen some guards disappear-- a lot of people run away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was-- one night, we were sleeping in the open field, and the guards were guarding us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And next day, we were marching to five holding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was carrying-- I couldn't walk anymore in these wooden shoes so I carried them on the shoulder-- my shoes and my jacket I was carrying on my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we marched to five holding like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And every 50 feet was a guard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one guard was seeing the other guard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as we turned, this guard didn't see this guard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I walked behind the guard there, and I run into a [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] door.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I see a little doorway we walked by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I run into a door to a house in a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was running away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And as I dropped my shoes in the column with the jacket, and I just slipped in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the whole column marched through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "As soon as they marched through, and I slipped in, a Shepherd dog started to bark, which he was chained up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I ran into a compartment where the pigs were-- in a compartment-- there were such compartments in there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was hiding under straw there, and the chickens run out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the owner comes out, and he sees here, because the dog was barking so loud.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the owner thought that the dog was barking because he hear trampling, from the wooden shoes that they were marching outside.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He starts to yell at the dog-- be quiet!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That dog was barking for me-- that I was-- I'm hiding over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But the owner did not know this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I was laying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
